I'm now integrating the data loading, cleaning, summarization, and saving into the notebook's structure. I've included all the code cells: loading the metadata and yield data, merging the datasets, filtering, calculating summary statistics with grouping, and then saving the result to a JSON file. The notebook is taking shape!

